gnatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","signer_pubkey":"ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAIHe3p+OG3L79IIh99qRBEkAEXaU+VbeQcSfhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"},{"content_hash":"8cb7bb6507ad89f1a1414201898e084b1958b66932b19e53d5a4a4b72a0d3fb0","event_uuid":"58f456b0-1b88-42b3-a22d-e01e5709a5b4","position":{"commit_sha":"89d0d3218d3af8560aa222c61240fef75dbd33ee","position":"1784862843052308305-58f456b0-1b88-42b3-a22d-e01e5709a5b4"},"signature":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","signer_pubkey":"ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAIHe3p+OG3L79IIh99qRBEkAEXaU+VbeQcSfhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"},{"content_hash":"64ce4551056f555ea2b157f6d1466890f6803758164fdf5990994f95db9e9a6e","event_uuid":"1fc257a7-72ca-42b0-9bd4-319aca5b56f8","position":{"commit_sha":"067b090b4b29fcbf97107b27347d3add725c48fd","position":"1784864241408940001-1fc257a7-72ca-42b0-9bd4-319aca5b56f8"},"signature":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","signer_pubkey":"ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAIHe3p+OG3L79IIh99qRBEkAEXaU+VbeQcSfhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"}],"bridge_alerts":[],"claim_harness":"claude-code_2-1-218_agent","claim_remote_session":null,"claimed_session":"0b793df7-72d9-4bad-8d4b-fce73214044d","comments":[{"author":"RebarBotNava","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","body":"Release prep on worktree release-0.10.1 (branched from origin/main @ ed8c747e8):\n- Version bump: pyproject.toml 0.10.0->0.10.1; server.json top-level + packages[0] -> 0.10.1. Lockstep verified: grep -c '0.10.1' pyproject.toml=1, server.json=2, no lingering 0.10.0.\n- CHANGELOG.md: generated [0.10.1] via 'make changelog VERSION=v0.10.1', hand-curated into Added/Changed/Fixed/Ops (maintenance release framing); fixed stale footer ([unreleased] was pinned at v0.8.0) and backfilled 0.9.0/0.9.1/0.10.0/0.10.1 compare-links.\n- Local gates GREEN: make lint (ruff+format+zizmor+actionlint+DCO), make typecheck (mypy, 379 files clean), python -m build (nava_rebar-0.10.1 wheel+sdist), 'twine check dist/*' PASSED on both artifacts.\n- make test running.","timestamp":1784862511544964001},{"author":"RebarBotNava","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","body":"Pushed release commit a7fde21 to Gerrit -> change 952 (https://rebar.solutions.navateam.com/c/rebar/+/952). Trailers verified: Change-Id present, DCO Signed-off-by RebarBotNava <joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com>, rebar-ticket resolves to 5ac8. Local make test: 7107 passed / 1 environmental teardown artifact (.tickets-tracker symlink flagged by the REPO_ROOT leak detector under the make-worktree store symlink; the test passes in isolation and is unrelated to the version-only diff). Awaiting LLM-Review +1 and Verified +1.","timestamp":1784864241408940001}],"created_at":1784861019725927001,"creation_channel":"cli","deps":[],"description":"## Summary\nCut the 0.10.1 patch release of rebar per docs/releasing.md. This is a fix/patch bump from 0.10.0, covering the ~36 commits landed on main since v0.10.0 (reconciler Backend-port scalar surfaces, plan-review/close-gate hardening, code-health analyzers scc/lizard/jscpd, review-bot token accounting, and assorted fixes).\n\n## Plan\n1. Fresh worktree from origin/main (git worktree add / make worktree).\n2. Bump versions in lockstep: pyproject.toml [project].version; server.json top-level version AND every packages[].version -> 0.10.1. server.json has exactly ONE packages[] entry, so a correct bump yields two 0.10.1 occurrences in that file. The release authorize job runs release_guards.py version-lockstep and fails the build on any mismatch.\n3. CHANGELOG.md: prepend the [0.10.1] section via 'make changelog VERSION=v0.10.1', hand-curate the generated top section, add the [0.10.1] compare-link footer.\n4. Local gates, run with the worktree venv on PATH: 'make lint && make typecheck && make test', then build+validate the artifact metadata exactly as the runbook (docs/releasing.md L259) and release.yml specify: 'python -m build && python -m twine check dist/*'. twine is not a dev extra in pyproject; invoke it as the CI lock does via 'pipx run twine check dist/*' (or 'uvx twine check dist/*') if 'python -m twine' is absent in the worktree venv, so the glob-targeted metadata check actually runs against the built wheel+sdist.\n5. Commit with 'rebar-ticket: zincoid-panoramic-eeve' + DCO sign-off trailers; push 'git push gerrit HEAD:refs/for/main'; earn LLM-Review +1 AND Verified +1; then Submit (POST /a/changes/<n>/submit as RebarBotNava).\n6. Fast-forward the worktree to merged main; dispatch the release from main: 'gh workflow run release.yml --ref main -f version=0.10.1' and approve the pypi environment deployment when prompted (required-reviewers gate). PyPI is immutable — if the published artifact is defective, yank it and ship 0.10.2.\n7. Verify the channels with the proving commands below.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Version-lockstep holds: 'grep -c 0.10.1 pyproject.toml' >=1 and 'grep -c 0.10.1 server.json' == 2 (top-level + the single packages[] entry) on the release commit; equivalently release_guards.py version-lockstep passes in the authorize job.\n- [ ] CHANGELOG.md carries a curated release section: 'grep -E \"^## \\[0\\.10\\.1\\]\" CHANGELOG.md' matches.\n- [ ] Release commit landed on main through Gerrit with both gate votes green: the Gerrit change shows LLM-Review +1 AND Verified +1 and status MERGED, and 'git log origin/main --oneline | grep -i \"release 0.10.1\"' finds it.\n- [ ] 0.10.1 published to PyPI: 'curl -s https://pypi.org/pypi/nava-rebar/json | python3 -c \"import json,sys;print(json.load(sys.stdin)[\\\"info\\\"][\\\"version\\\"])\"' prints 0.10.1.\n- [ ] v0.10.1 tag + GitHub Release created at the released main SHA: 'gh release view v0.10.1 --json tagName,targetCommitish,isLatest' shows the tag, marked Latest.\n\n## Out of scope / automated follow-ups (no executor action required)\n- Homebrew tap self-bump (navapbc/homebrew-rebar autobump.yml, scheduled every 6h) and the MCP-registry publish job (mcp_registry in release.yml, needs: publish) run automatically after publish; verifying them is not a release-blocking acceptance criterion for this ticket.\n\n## Attestation evidence\n- The above acceptance criteria are proven in-session by the quoted shell/gh/curl commands whose outputs are recorded as comments on this ticket, plus the Gerrit change number and its +1/+1 vote outcome and MERGED status.","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[{"path":"pyproject.toml","reason":"bump [project].version 0.10.0 -> 0.10.1"},{"path":"server.json","reason":"bump top-level version and every packages[].version to 0.10.1 (version-lockstep)"},{"path":"CHANGELOG.md","reason":"prepend curated [0.10.1] release section + compare-link footer"}],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[],"parent_id":null,"parent_status_uuid":"8d5eab07-c781-41cf-8e77-5b95bf2b9dd4","plan_review_phase":"execution","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":2,"reverts":[],"status":"in_progress","tags":[],"ticket_id":"5ac8-96d1-4691-49a5","ticket_type":"task","title":"Release 0.10.1 (patch/fix version)","verify_commands":[]},"source_event_uuids":["b30f28c9-ed26-4f59-ae55-757e48d37c4b","e9c3bc04-320e-47ad-9f02-f99b3ee7e5ed","c32f0f54-65ef-4a09-9f93-65757755d82a","b48bd8fb-65d0-41c9-aeec-cb65d4ca10e7","c78b97d7-159f-40e4-bc44-2816a53b7e1b","8d5eab07-c781-41cf-8e77-5b95bf2b9dd4","7e397e3d-96ed-410f-8b1a-a08cd6e3f24c","421adda4-60a2-4d3f-ac92-97996798564d","58f456b0-1b88-42b3-a22d-e01e5709a5b4","1fc257a7-72ca-42b0-9bd4-319aca5b56f8"]},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-